Overview

The Vending System CLI is a terminal-based application developed in Python that simulates a basic vending machine workflow. It focuses on core programming logic, user input handling, and file-based transaction tracking.

Purpose

This project demonstrates foundational programming concepts such as control flow, data validation, and file handling in a structured command-line environment.

Key Features
Product selection via CLI interface
Stock validation and management
Payment simulation and change calculation
Transaction logging using file storage
